          <p><strong>Not All Sump Pumps Are Created Equal - Here's What You Need to Know</strong></p>
          
          <h3>1. Submersible Sump Pumps (Most Popular Choice)</h3>
          <p>Submersible pumps sit completely underwater in your sump pit. They're our most recommended option for Toronto homes because:</p>
