            <li><strong>Status monitoring</strong> - Alarms alert you to activation</li>
            <li><strong>Dual pump protection</strong> - Can also activate if primary fails</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Best for:</strong> ALL Toronto homes - power outages during storms are common</p>
          <p><strong>Investment:</strong> $600-$1,200 including battery</p>

